{"kanda":6,"sarga":100,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौहतौदृष्टवातुराक्ष ।तस्मिंश्चनिहतेवीरेविरूपाक्षेमहाबले आविवेशमहान् क्रोधोरावणंतुमहामृधे ।सूतं सञ्चोदयामास वाक्यं चेदमुवाच ह","trans":"On seeing Mahodara and Mahaparsva killed in the great war, Virupaksha of extraordinary might also killed, Ravana was highly infuriated and addressed the charioteer in the following words.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसौ","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौ","m":"Mahodara and Mahaparsva"},{"d":"हतौ","m":"killed"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"महाबले","m":"of extraordinary might"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षे","m":"Virupaksha"},{"d":"निहते","m":"killed"},{"d":"महामृधे","m":"in that great war"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"महान्","m":"highly"},{"d":"क्रोधः","m":"infuriated"},{"d":"आविवेश","m":"urged"},{"d":"सूतम्","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"सञ्चोदयामास","m":"addressed"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम् च","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौहतौदृष्टवातुराक्ष ।तस्मिंश्चनिहतेवीरेविरूपाक्षेमहाबले आविवेशमहान् क्रोधोरावणंतुमहामृधे ।सूतं सञ्चोदयामास वाक्यं चेदमुवाच ह","trans":"On seeing Mahodara and Mahaparsva killed in the great war, Virupaksha of extraordinary might also killed, Ravana was highly infuriated and addressed the charioteer in the following words.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसौ","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौ","m":"Mahodara and Mahaparsva"},{"d":"हतौ","m":"killed"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"महाबले","m":"of extraordinary might"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षे","m":"Virupaksha"},{"d":"निहते","m":"killed"},{"d":"महामृधे","m":"in that great war"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"महान्","m":"highly"},{"d":"क्रोधः","m":"infuriated"},{"d":"आविवेश","m":"urged"},{"d":"सूतम्","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"सञ्चोदयामास","m":"addressed"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम् च","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"निहतानाममात्यानांरुद्धस्यनगरस्य च ।दुःखमेवापनेष्